      "description": "Experimental validation of CFD hemolysis predictions against in-vitro measurements for adult CPB flow rates (2.0–6.0 L/min) and haematocrit 35–45 %. Conducted prior to Q4 2025 envelope expansion. RH index predictions within ±12 % of measured values across all 5 operating points. Dataset frozen 2023-09-15.",
      "generatedAtTime": "2023-09-15T00:00:00Z",
