      "factorType": "Model form",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Formal model form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2. The Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis model and SST k-omega turbulence closure are established for blood pump applications. Scoped out per MRL 2 requirements."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
