      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; nominal input values used.",
      "rationale": "Sensitivity analysis on model inputs (fluid viscosity, density, hemolysis model coefficients) not required at MRL 2. Nominal values from literature and device specifications applied. Scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 1."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
